StepCounter stepCounter = await StepCounter.GetDefaultAsync();
StepCounterReading steps = await stepCounter.GetStepCountAtAsync( DateTime.Now.AddHours( -2 ) );

The following example shows how to get the  and fetch steps from past hour.

StepCounter stepCounter = await StepCounter.GetDefaultAsync();
IList<StepCounterReading> steps = await stepCounter.GetStepCountHistoryAsync( DateTime.Now.AddHours( -1 ), TimeSpan.FromHours( 1 ) );

